description: Chafer. Superbly designed and manufactured induction chafers with distinctive handles create a sensation in front-of-house presentations, as well as for serving at buffets, corporate dining rooms, catered events, and more. Durable, 18/10 stainless steel chafer is manufactured with three layers, two of steel and one of aluminum for superior cooking and excellent durability; the interior layer of stainless steel promotes flavor preservation and corrosion-resistance; the exterior layer is magnetic stainless steel for use on a variety of different cooktops; the middle layer is aluminum to give the chafer outstanding heat distribution and to help make sure food cooks thoroughly. Two different handle configurations are available, one with two handles - one on either side - and the skillet configuration with a long handle; all handles are riveted to the pot and allow for easy lifting and transport; attractively shaped lid is also engineered for ease of use.
